sg":"忘記了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032356141891574a3fe13bef0736010cb9c0115e","tid":700270,"uid":62650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"其實經常選擇性男女平等..."},{"pid":"359f41969732e279cc8d9ff5cb48f0225d64c9a4","tid":700270,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8bc39513d472909a3aeae80f2b11495932441b3","tid":700270,"uid":172607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:23:09.000Z","msg":"所以結婚前要諗清楚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:50:17.000Z","msg":"X2...但又想有後代...唔通單性繁殖咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62210f2102ef68bfa59371165a12b4eabbbb95d","tid":700270,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:34:24.000Z","msg":"拍拖果時 :<br />\n男方比哂-&gt;無問題<br />\nAA制-&gt;依個都唔係男人黎，無風度，算<br />\n女方比哂-&gt;無可能<br />\n<br />\n結左婚就求撚期啦"},{"pid":"a46f250c314cf243447aae5c406d8bf6469a65c9","tid":700270,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db73eafea4af92c725a67183366f328ce47fef72","tid":700270,"uid":5462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"有時d人真係好小家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水電煤小朋友雜費都唔知點計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"女人：要我出我自己果份？咁小家架<br />\n女人：我出左自己果份我好現代女性好獨立呀。"}]}